description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Lower Body Strength with Bands' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement. The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Build strength in your lower body with Peter while using a mini band.

Note: A mini-band is recommended....
